            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a bowl, then add the <strong>cucumber matchsticks</strong>, <strong>grated carrot </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>– this is your<strong> quick-pickled salad</strong></p><p>Bash your <strong>Fable pulled mushrooms</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> to flatten them</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-2-1678455560497-x200.jpg",
