          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>peanuts</strong> very finely – this is your <strong>peanut crumble</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>tamarind paste </strong>and <strong>vegan mayo </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>tamarind mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-3-1678455592501-x200.jpg",
