      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your buns, fill each <strong>bao bun</strong> with a little <strong>quick-pickled salad</strong> and the <strong>sweet chilli fable mushrooms</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> peanut crumble</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips </strong>and<strong> lime wedge </strong>to the side with the <strong>tamarind mayo </strong>and the<strong> remaining quick-pickled salad </strong>and garnish with the<strong> reserved coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
